@startuml
title Sequence Diagram. Успешный ответ ML

actor "Пользователь" as User
participant "Client Application" as Client
participant "Recommendation Service" as RecService
participant "ML Recommendation Service" as ML

User -> Client : Открывает рекомендации
Client -> RecService : POST /api/v1/recommendations
RecService -> RecService : Проверить запрос и права
RecService -> ML : Запрос рекомендаций
activate ML
ML --> RecService : 200, items, confidence >= threshold
deactivate ML
RecService -> RecService : Проверить ответ и confidence
RecService --> Client : 200, source = ML, items
Client --> User : Показать рекомендации

@enduml

